---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Alert Energy - Energy Consulting Since 2014" description="Alert Energy has served leading property brands since 2014. Learn about our team, credentials, and approach to energy consulting.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-navy-800 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">About Us</p>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Optimizing Energy<br/>Since 2014.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-navy-200 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Alert Energy is an energy consulting firm built on the principle that good data drives
          good decisions. For over a decade, we have served utilities, engineering firms, and
          building owners across North America -- bringing rigorous analysis and practical
          expertise to complex energy challenges.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STORY -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy-800 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Founded in 2014, Alert Energy grew out of a simple observation: the energy industry is full
            of data, but too few firms bring genuine analytical rigor to the problems that matter most
            to building owners and operators.
          </p>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We started by working with some of the largest and most demanding property portfolios in
            North America -- names like Westfield Properties, Macy's, and Mandarin Oriental Hotels.
            These clients taught us that energy consulting is not about cutting corners or checking boxes.
            It is about getting the numbers right, understanding what they mean, and translating them
            into decisions that save money and reduce risk.
          </p>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">
            Today, we bring that same institutional-grade precision to building owners navigating
            the growing web of regulated energy benchmarking requirements. Whether you are a
            single-building owner in Toronto or a property manager with assets across multiple
            jurisdictions, we approach your compliance with the same rigor we bring to our largest
            enterprise clients.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Stats -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center border border-slate-100">
              <p class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">12+</p>
              <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm mt-1">Years in Business</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center border border-slate-100">
              <p class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">5</p>
              <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm mt-1">City Markets</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center border border-slate-100">
              <p class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">3</p>
              <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm mt-1">Countries Served</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 text-center border border-slate-100">
              <p class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">Tier 1</p>
              <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm mt-1">Client Portfolio</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Quote -->
          <div class="bg-navy-800 rounded-xl p-8">
            <p class="text-navy-200 leading-relaxed italic mb-4">
              "We do not just file reports. We treat every benchmarking engagement as an audit
              of your building's energy health -- because the data you submit today shapes the
              decisions you make tomorrow."
            </p>
            <p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm">Alert Energy Team</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES OVERVIEW -->
  <section id="services" class="bg-slate-50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy-800 mb-3">Our Capabilities</h2>
        <p class="text-navy-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          While our current campaign focuses on regulated benchmarking, our team and network
          cover the full spectrum of building energy services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Service 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">Energy Accounting</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            M&V, regulated benchmarking, sub-metering, and utility bill analysis.
            We make sure your energy data is accurate and actionable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">Energy Economics</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Program design, evaluation (EM&V), procurement strategy, and energy systems planning.
            We help you make smarter financial decisions about energy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">Auditing, Testing & Commissioning</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Comprehensive energy audits, building testing, and commissioning services
            to verify your building performs as designed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">Regulations & Permitting</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Navigating energy regulations, permitting requirements, and certification
            processes across multiple jurisdictions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 5 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">Health & Safety Compliance</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Ensuring your energy projects meet health and safety standards,
            protecting your building and your people.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 6 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-50 text-amber-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy-800 mb-2">Trusted Network</h3>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Our network of vetted professionals covers the complete building lifecycle
            from discovery and origination through planning, design, and project management.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NOTABLE CLIENTS -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy-800 mb-3">Clients Who Trust Us</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center border border-slate-100">
          <p class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-navy-800 mb-3">Westfield Properties</p>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Multi-property portfolio energy compliance across multiple jurisdictions and building types.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center border border-slate-100">
          <p class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-navy-800 mb-3">Macy's</p>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Enterprise-scale energy accounting and benchmarking for one of America's largest retail portfolios.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center border border-slate-100">
          <p class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-navy-800 mb-3">Mandarin Oriental</p>
          <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Premium hospitality energy management and sustainability reporting to the highest standards.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-navy-800 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Ready to work with us?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-navy-200 text-lg mb-8">
        Whether you need benchmarking compliance or a full energy strategy, we are here to help.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-amber-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-amber-700 transition-colors text-lg">
        Get In Touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
